WEBVTT

00:00.822 --> 00:02.055
<i>Previously on</i> Medium...

00:02.106 --> 00:04.390
Joe can't know what
I'm about to tell you.

00:06.661 --> 00:09.830
I'm pretty
sick, Allison.

00:09.897 --> 00:11.398
My odds are 60%.

00:11.465 --> 00:15.602
I was having a dream
about you.

00:15.670 --> 00:17.103
We were,

00:17.171 --> 00:19.539
we were in your living room
in Grosse Pointe.

00:19.607 --> 00:22.843
It was, uh, it was
Ariel, Bridgette, Marie.

00:22.910 --> 00:25.579
And-And Bridgette had just

00:25.646 --> 00:27.480
graduated
from college.

00:28.583 --> 00:29.783
You did a good thing.

00:29.851 --> 00:31.618
Even though I lied.

00:31.686 --> 00:34.354
Ah, don't worry about it.

