00:44.598 --> 00:45.949
Morning, Bob.

00:46.033 --> 00:46.967
Morning, Tom.

00:47.034 --> 00:48.001
Ready to
get to work?

00:48.069 --> 00:48.985
You betcha.

00:49.070 --> 00:52.772
Let's go for
day number 24,838.

00:52.840 --> 00:55.041
Cool offices!

00:55.109 --> 00:58.111
What are you guys
working on in here?

00:58.179 --> 00:59.829
Look, I don't know
who let you in,

00:59.914 --> 01:01.648
but it's not cool
for you to be here.

01:01.716 --> 01:03.550
Now, I'm gonna let you
off with a warning,

01:03.618 --> 01:07.053
but the next time I look up,
you best be gone.

01:08.689 --> 01:10.724
Nice light.

01:10.791 --> 01:13.793
How often you guys have
to change the bulbs in here?

01:13.861 --> 01:15.428
What is the matter
with you two?

01:15.479 --> 01:17.564
Did you not
hear my friend?

01:17.632 --> 01:19.766
Hit the road.

01:21.502 --> 01:24.571
So what are you guys
getting all upset about?

01:24.638 --> 01:26.039
We're just new
to the neighborhood,

01:26.107 --> 01:27.324
wanted to say "hey."

01:27.408 --> 01:28.642
New to the
neighborhood?

01:28.709 --> 01:29.910
This isn't your
neighborhood.

01:29.977 --> 01:31.494
You're not even
supposed to be here.

01:31.579 --> 01:32.746
Why not?

01:35.166 --> 01:37.217
This is bad.

01:37.285 --> 01:38.484
We should call Central.

01:38.536 --> 01:39.486
On it.

01:39.553 --> 01:40.987
You're calling Central?

01:41.038 --> 01:42.372
Awesome!

01:42.456 --> 01:44.624
Hey, you think they'd call out
and get us some pizzas?

01:44.675 --> 01:46.059
Oh, my God.

01:46.127 --> 01:48.011
They're multiplying
really fast.

01:48.095 --> 01:49.346
Pizza?

01:49.430 --> 01:51.765
Anybody interested in
some pineapple on top?

01:51.832 --> 01:52.966
It's just ringing
and ringing.

01:53.017 --> 01:54.100
Nobody's picking up.

01:54.168 --> 01:55.602
Can I see a show of hands?

01:55.669 --> 01:56.770
How many for pineapple?

02:00.441 --> 02:01.975
Get out.

02:02.026 --> 02:03.059
Get out!

02:03.144 --> 02:04.844
You're not supposed
to be here!

02:04.895 --> 02:07.314
None of you are
supposed to be here!

02:07.365 --> 02:08.648
Get out!

02:08.716 --> 02:11.584
None of you are
supposed to be here!

02:11.652 --> 02:13.887
Leave us alone,
all of you!

02:13.955 --> 02:16.356
Get out!

02:16.407 --> 02:18.291
I'm truly sorry, Marjorie.

02:20.044 --> 02:24.247
We had no idea things had gotten
this bad this quickly.

02:24.332 --> 02:27.133
I know this isn't the diagnosis
you were hoping for,

02:27.201 --> 02:30.070
the diagnosis you expected.

02:30.137 --> 02:33.073
If you have any questions
or if you just need time

02:33.140 --> 02:35.709
to think about everything
you've been told...

02:37.712 --> 02:39.813
No.

02:39.880 --> 02:43.183
I'm fine.

02:43.250 --> 02:44.851
Really.

02:44.919 --> 02:47.754
Are you sure?

02:47.822 --> 02:50.357
Absolutely.

02:59.367 --> 03:02.335
Mom?

03:02.403 --> 03:04.070
It's not even 7:00 here.

03:04.138 --> 03:06.406
You all right?

03:06.457 --> 03:08.458
Hold on, hold on.

